caption.p: Effect of Cuminum cyminum seed essential oil on the motility of M. javanica J2s after immersion in test solutions at concentrations of 62.5, 125, 250, and 500 μL/L for 12 h (T0), transferred in water, and counted after 12 (T12), 24 (T24) and 48 (T48) h. * Values for each concentration followed by the same letter are not significantly different according to Tukey’s HSD test at p < 0.05.
